/app (root folder on your host)
├── start_bot.py            # Entry point
├── nija_client.py          # Root shim for backward compatibility
├── app/                    # Folder for main app code
│   ├── __init__.py        # Marks `app` as a Python package
│   └── nija_client.py      # Robust Coinbase client class
├── .env                    # Environment variables
